03:09.955 --> 03:12.289
Poor old Joe hoffsinger.

03:12.357 --> 03:15.994
Here today, gone tomorrow.
That's the way it is.

03:16.061 --> 03:18.262
Another victim of the grim weeper.

03:20.533 --> 03:22.600
Sure makes you think about life, though.

03:22.668 --> 03:24.769
Jeez, you get married,
you work your butt off

03:24.837 --> 03:26.504
