get along with a kid like Bernard,

04:19.091 --> 04:21.125
with his painted toenails,
carrying a purse,

04:21.192 --> 04:22.861
and whiskers down to his bellybutton?

04:24.396 --> 04:26.030
He's a musician.

04:26.098 --> 04:29.934
