into the business.

04:51.556 --> 04:53.858
And it was a very good business.

04:53.925 --> 04:55.126
What business was that?

04:55.194 --> 04:57.028
He was an exterminator.

04:58.030 --> 05:00.165
You should've seen his truck.

05:00.232 --> 05:02.466
It was covered with all kinds of pictures

05:02.534 --> 05:04.068
of the different kinds of bugs

05:04.136 --> 05:06.004
