don't mean nothing to you.

07:50.034 --> 07:53.036
I'm telling you right now, there's
a big "hate your parents" movement

07:53.104 --> 07:54.838
going on in this country

07:54.906 --> 07:57.375
in the U.S. of a., but it wasn't
an American that started it.

07:57.442 --> 08:00.678
