by the name of Sigmund froos.

08:03.382 --> 08:07.652
Freud only said that parents
can create a lot of problems.

08:07.720 --> 08:09.186
Oh, he's wacky.

08:09.255 --> 08:12.190
Parents create children and
children create the problems,

08:12.257 --> 08:14.024
including you, little girl.

08:14.092 --> 08:16.394
