08:16.461 --> 08:18.896
Well, tip a glance to your right there.

08:20.465 --> 08:22.132
That's not funny, arch.

08:22.200 --> 08:24.735
No, it's sad and it's terrible.

08:24.803 --> 08:27.138
Daddy, I didn't ask to be born.

08:27.206 --> 08:29.840
Oh, well, now you're here, I
mean, what're we gonna do,

08:29.908 --> 08:33.443
